== Botshelo jwa gagwe ==

Lebo Mathosa o tsholetswe ko [[Daveyton]], toropo e e kontle ga Benoni. Masika a gagwe morago a ne a fodugela ko [[Johannesburg]] kwa Lebo a tseneng sekolo ko sekolong se segolwane sa St. Mary's. Lebo o simolotse go opela a nale dingwaga di le supa mo mokgatho o o opela wa kereke. E rile masika a gagwe a fudugela ko Johannesburg, o ne a bona moopelo wa bubblegum, o e leng mofuta wa disco-infused pop o o neng o tumisitswe ke batho ba go tshwana [[Brenda Fassie]], ba ne Mathosa a ba tsaya e le bagaka.<ref>[http://www.thenewblackmagazine.com/view.aspx?index=465 Lebo Mathosa – South African Singing Sensation.]</ref>

